【Important】Details of the MV Listing Start Date and Whitelist Round 2 End Date

Dec. 29, 2021

Metaverse (MV) Token Listing Start Date Announced

With the IDO of TRUSTPAD, the start date for the listing of our MV tokens has been set for January 20, 2022.

It will be listed on 2 DEXs, Uniswap and QuickSwap, on the same day, as stated in the roadmap.

The winners of the current “Whitelist Round 2” and previous Whitelist campaigns will receive their tokens right before the above listing.

Campaign Schedule for Whitelist Round 2

The campaign schedule for Whitelist Round 2 has been finalized.

End date of the campaign
January 13, 2022

Emails sent to the winners of the campaign
January 14, 2022

Application period for winners to purchase tokens
Jan. 14, 2022 – Jan. 19, 2022

Token distribution to token purchasers
January 20, 2022

* Please note that we will not be able to accept any applications after the application period.
* If you did not receive an e-mail on January 14, 2022, please understand that you were not chosen in the lottery.

Caution

Restricted countries: United States of America,China,Hong Kong, and all sanctioned OFAC countries(DR Congo,Iran,Myanmar,Sudan,Iraq,Ivory Coast,North Korea,Syria,Zimbabwe,Cuba,Balarus,Liberia)
